ppsspp (1.20.4-2foundry1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Rebuild against ubuntu:26.04's ffmpeg 8 / libavcodec62. The 26.04
    repos moved from ffmpeg 7.x (libavcodec61) to ffmpeg 8.x (libavcodec62)
    on 2026-05-26, making the 1foundry1 binary uninstallable. No source
    changes — dpkg-shlibdeps auto-resolves to libavcodec62 in the new
    ubuntu:26.04 build environment.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Mon, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

ppsspp (1.20.4-1foundry1) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial packaging for Foundry Linux apt repo.
  * Uses system ffmpeg, SDL2, libpng, zstd, miniupnpc, freetype, rapidjson,
    libzip, snappy in place of upstream bundled/submodule copies.
  * Vulkan + OpenGL rendering enabled. Discord RPC disabled.
  * Binary renamed from upstream PPSSPPSDL to ppsspp.
  * Source: https://github.com/hrydgard/ppsspp/releases/tag/v1.20.4
  * Commit: fa50bb1976065c4f8b1b47af227d367fe9771555

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Sat, 23 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
